{"tid":2018542,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[靈異]屯門公園有龜從天而降！！！","createTime":"2020-05-15T16:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T08:39:03.000Z","uid":304415,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4ec9e8d0337f94688d5f71b45c5e07555d6d52","tid":2018542,"uid":304415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:18:07.000Z","msg":"今日九點幾 行行下屯門公園<br />\n有好大舊野跌咗落嚟 遠睇以為係芒果定果實 <br />\n再行近少少 先發現原來係隻龜<br />\n雖然咁高跌落嚟 都冇碎冇爆到 反咗肚<br />\n但係啲頭手同腳就縮哂入去<br />\n之後幫佢反返個身 龜背朝天<br />\n<br />\n發現係龜嗰刻有啲驚 會唔會係有痴線佬放咗隻龜上樹上面 之後佢自己跌落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望佢平平安安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果真係有人突登放隻龜上去 條虐畜仆街不得好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444c0ae8229ec17f0add99813c5d82a2c4cc974a","tid":2018542,"uid":332452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2106d7788b660d90aea6b9b7d0683c5b692adc","tid":2018542,"uid":153644,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15